name: DeepBoys_2.5D
description:

If you support me, I will make many AI male models and try to improve them more beautifully.

Deep boys 2.5D ver.2 creates a more mature male face.

  • Sampling method : Eular a / DPM++ SDE Karras

  • Clip skip : 4~6

  • Hires.fix upscaler : SwinIR_4x

  • CFG Scale : 7~9

  • VAE : vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned
